sdata (0.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Implement AND, OR, and XOR boolean operators.
  * Fix END SELECT parsing and blank line handling inside SELECT blocks.
  * Fix SELECT block parsing and multi-line support in REPL.
  * Route error/warning messages to both output file and stderr.
  * Allow variable and expression bounds in DIM command.
  * Fix case-sensitivity bug in OBS and LAG functions.
  * Expand arrays in ARRAY command constituent list.
  * Fix SORT to save output dataset and print completion message.
  * Replace heapsort with stable merge sort.
  * SlackBuild: use gnatmake instead of gprbuild.
  * Remove unused sciada dependency from all build systems.
  * Add README.md.

